<div class="container mt-3">
    <h2 class="text-center mb-4" style="font-size: 2.8rem; font-weight: bold; color: #2c3e50;">Education Background</h2>

    <div style="margin-top: 4rem;">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center" style="max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto;">
            <!-- Image section -->
            <img src="~/images/Xiamen_University_logo.svg.png" 
                alt="Xiamen University Logo"
                style="height: 140px; align-self: center; border-radius: 50%; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); padding: 0.75rem;">
            
            <!-- Card Section -->
            <div class="card" 
                style="flex-grow: 1; margin-left: 2rem; background-color: #F6F5EF; border-radius: 24px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); overflow: hidden;">
                <div class="card-body" style="padding: 2.75rem; text-align: justify;">
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-4">
                        <div class="edu-icon me-3" style="font-size: 2.8rem; color: #3498db;">
                            <i class="fas fa-university"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="card-title mb-1" style="font-size: 2rem; color: #2c3e50;">Xiamen University</h3>
                            <h4 class="card-subtitle" style="font-size: 1.3rem; color: #555;">Bachelor of Software Engineering</h4>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <hr style="border-top: 1px solid #d5d5d5; margin: 1.25rem 0;">
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
                        <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt me-2" style="color: #e67e22;"></i>
                        <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 1.1rem;">2022–2026</span>
                    </div>
                    <ul style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #333; margin-top: 1.25rem; text-align: justify; list-style-type: disc; padding-left: 1.75rem;">
                        <li><span class="badge bg-primary me-2">Full-Stack</span> Specialized in Full-Stack Development, mastering both front-end and back-end technologies.</li>
                        <li><span class="badge bg-success me-2">AI</span> Conducted research on large language models and recommendation systems, focusing on innovative solutions.</li>
                        <li><span class="badge bg-warning text-dark me-2">ML</span> Engaged in projects that integrated AI and machine learning to enhance user experience and system efficiency.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


